Treasury balances at the FederalReserve fell on April 2 to 3.775 billion dlrs from 4.602billion dlrs on the previous business day, the Treasury said inits latest budget statement.    Balances in tax and loan note accounts fell to 6.493billion dlrs from 6.495 billion dlrs on the same respectivedays.    The Treasury's operating cash balance totaled 10.268billion dlrs on April 2 compared with 11.097 billion dlrs onApril 1. Reuter&#3;